snippet.title: Celebrities Furiously React To Working With Amber Heard in Aquaman 2
snippet.description:
Amber Heard recently shared her excitement about starring in Aquaman 2 but stars like Jason Momoa and Angelina Jolie don’t feel the same. Find out how celebrities are reacting to Amber being allowed to keep her role in the film.

Amber Heard’s friends also disapprove of her role in Aquaman 2. Here’s what they had to say: https://youtu.be/SouAGT5OY9s
